Welcome to Duke Country!
Gloucester County Public Schools are closed to all students and guests.
Continuous updates will be shared as they become available and deemed appropriate.
The Main Office will be open on Mondays and Wednesdays from 9:00 am to 1:00 pm for phone calls. If you need to visit the building, please make an appointment.
Students who are staying after school must be with a teacher or sponsor.
Those students who are not with a teacher or sponsor will be escorted out of the building.




